Message-Driven Beans (2 files)\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTBroker3MDB.java** - Processes order messages from queue\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTStreamer3MDB.java** - Processes quote updates from topic\n\n## Messaging (3 files)\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessageProducerService.java** - Reactive messaging producer\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/OrderMessage.java** - POJO for order messages\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/QuoteUpdateMessage.java** - POJO for quote update messages\n\n## Startup (1 file)\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/startup/DatabasePopulator.java** - Populates database on startup\n\n## Utilities (7 files)\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/FinancialUtils.java** - Financial calculation utilities\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/KeyBlock.java** - Primary key block management\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/Log.java** - Logging utility\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/MDBStats.java** - MDB statistics tracking\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/RecentQuotePriceChangeList.java** - Tracks recent quote changes\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TimerStat.java** - Timer statistics bean\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TradeConfig.java** - Configuration and constants (425 lines)\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java** - Runtime mode annotation literal\n\n## Web (1 file)\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/TradeAppResource.java** - HTML web interface (414 lines)\n\n## Test Files (3 files)\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/test/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/TradeResourceTest.java** - Tests for TradeResource\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/test/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessagingResourceTest.java** - Tests for messaging REST API\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/test/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessagingTest.java** - Tests for messaging functionality\n\n## Key Migration Notes Found Throughout\n\nThe codebase shows a comprehensive migration from Jakarta EE to Quarkus with these major changes:\n\n1. **JMS to Reactive Messaging**: Traditional JMS MessageListener classes replaced with @Incoming annotations from MicroProfile Reactive Messaging\n2. **Namespace Migration**: All `javax.*` imports changed to `jakarta.*`\n3. **CDI Qualifiers**: Extensive use of CDI qualifiers for runtime mode selection (@TradeDB, @TradeEJB, etc.)\n4. **Entity Management**: JPA entities retained but using Quarkus-managed EntityManager\n5. **REST Services**: JAX-RS resources using Jakarta REST APIs\n6. **Async Processing**: Multiple modes (SYNCH, ASYNCH, ASYNCH_2PHASE) supported\n7. **Database**: Supports both JPA and JDBC implementations\n8. **Testing**: Uses Quarkus testing framework with REST-assured\n\nAll files have been completely read and contain detailed migration notes explaining the changes from the original Jakarta EE implementation to Quarkus."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6dc8c70c-c917-4a3c-9449-19451948009a","uuid":"4dbc7aa6-ccdb-4d74-921f-f103f7e46def"}
