{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_018Jdovvh93AJK3zuLEM7wV8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration from **Quarkus 3.17.0 to Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty)** is complete. Here's a final summary:\n\n## Migration Results\n\n- **17/17 smoke tests passing**\n- **Framework**: Quarkus 3.17.0 → Jakarta EE 10 on Open Liberty\n- **Packaging**: JAR → WAR\n- **All business logic preserved**\n\n## Key Changes Made\n\n| Area | Before (Quarkus) | After (Jakarta EE) |\n|------|-------------------|---------------------|\n| Dependencies | quarkus-* BOM | jakarta.jakartaee-api 10.0.0 |\n| Messaging | SmallRye Reactive Messaging | CDI Events (`@ObservesAsync`) |\n| Scheduling | `@Scheduled(every=\"20s\")` | `@Schedule(second=\"*/20\",...)` |\n| Startup | `@Observes StartupEvent` | `@Singleton @Startup @PostConstruct` |\n| DataSource | `@Inject AgroalDataSource` | `@Resource(name=\"jdbc/TradeDataSource\")` |\n| Persistence | `@Inject EntityManager` | `@PersistenceContext EntityManager` |\n| JSON | Jackson `@JsonIgnore` | JSON-B `@JsonbTransient` |\n| Concurrency | `@VirtualThreads` | `@Resource ManagedExecutorService` |\n| Runtime | Quarkus native | Open Liberty full-java17-openj9-ubi |\n\n## Errors Resolved\n\n1. Missing `PersistenceContext` import in TradeSLSBBean\n2. H2 v2 `INTEGER IDENTITY` syntax incompatibility → switched to `GenerationType.AUTO`\n3. EclipseLink OneToOne `mappedBy` navigation failure → JPQL helper query workaround\n4. EJB ORB registry warning → added `<basicRegistry>` to server.xml\n\nAll changes are documented in `CHANGELOG.md`."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":509,"cache_read_input_tokens":31929,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":509,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":484},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6dc8c70c-c917-4a3c-9449-19451948009a","uuid":"ade07